NAME

    Map::Tube::Bielefeld - interface to the Bielefeld Stadtbahn

DESCRIPTION

    It currently provides functionality to find the shortest route between
    the two given stations.

CONSTRUCTOR

        use Map::Tube::Bielefeld;
        my $tube = Map::Tube::Bielefeld->new;

METHODS

 get_shortest_route(START, END)

    This method expects two parameters START and END station name. Station
    names are case insensitive. The station sequence from START to END is
    returned.

        use Map::Tube::Bielefeld;
        my $tube = Map::Tube::Bielefeld->new;
        my $route = $tube->get_shortest_route('', '');
        print "Route: $route\n";

